{"tid":290720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"醫療輔助隊暫停在郊野公園提供急救服務","createTime":"2017-06-20T03:44:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-20T04:28:09.000Z","uid":30873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4bbb18ba4814d5bb4c0d2c448e7131c237a3650f","tid":290720,"uid":30873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T03:44:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">醫療輔助隊將於7月1日暫停在郊野公園提供急救服務</span></span><br />\n<br />\n醫療輔助隊將於2017年7月1日暫停所有於郊野公園提供的急救服務 (香港仔郊野公園除外) 。郊野公園的救護車服務亦將於當日全部暫停，而救護電單車服務則會維持正常，敬請留意。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/20/114420_3607d95a7144440f81f554e5789af425.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F20%2F114420_3607d95a7144440f81f554e5789af425.jpg&h=563f8e6c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d1ee8cea300fc4740e45b21705c568cb427e10f8","tid":290720,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T03:46:19.000Z","msg":"因為人手去晒正苦回歸活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3010ad8e4f6826acef73105ecd8ed73be108e36","tid":290720,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T03:47:13.000Z","msg":"比st. john 搞下化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73c5d825f4a4e09f0393ac69d9a8cced33672d77","tid":290720,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T03:53:48.000Z","msg":"有事咁點？"},{"pid":"97a17c2768116f8b64275c2c28923124e85ecaf6","tid":290720,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T04:01:18.000Z","msg":"乜佢地有車架咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見st.john仲多過佢地"},{"pid":"00a397562a1c6a6c25c40aace1e5343c457ddfc6","tid":290720,"uid":115415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T04:04:08.000Z","msg":"應該調哂去七一既活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clo